No, no, no.

00:29.039 --> 00:31.089
Move your hand, okay.

00:31.100 --> 00:33.060
I need you to look at this.

00:33.070 --> 00:35.000
Test it.

00:35.009 --> 00:36.049
No!

00:37.229 --> 00:38.219
Don't!

00:38.229 --> 00:40.109
Does she know who she is?

00:40.119 --> 00:43.140
Or shall I say what she is.

00:43.149 --> 00:46.020
If I ever see you again,

00:43.149 --> 00:46.020
I will kill you.

00:46.030 --> 00:47.159
You hear me Vanessa?

00:47.170 --> 00:50.149
My sister's sacrifice

00:47.170 --> 00:50.149
won't be for nothing.

01:02.159 --> 01:04.180
[birds chirping]

01:14.079 --> 01:16.010
[crash]

01:37.210 --> 01:40.060
[snarling]

01:52.069 --> 01:54.250
[vomiting]

02:02.069 --> 02:05.019
[loud screeching]

02:21.129 --> 02:23.139
[coughing]

02:28.050 --> 02:30.039
[panting]

02:49.050 --> 02:51.069
[hissing and snarling]

02:55.039 --> 02:57.079
I've made mistakes.

03:03.189 --> 03:06.169
Caused so much damage.

03:10.139 --> 03:12.259
[snarling]

03:12.270 --> 03:15.270
But now I understand.

03:19.150 --> 03:22.129
I was following the wrong path.

03:23.199 --> 03:25.240
The path of darkness.

03:26.210 --> 03:29.139
[snarling]

03:30.259 --> 03:33.050
Now I know the way.

03:43.229 --> 03:44.250
[snarls]

03:59.240 --> 04:04.120
[growling]

04:04.129 --> 04:07.060
My mind is clear.

04:07.259 --> 04:10.060
I'm not going to kill.

04:11.080 --> 04:13.099
Only salvage.

04:15.219 --> 04:19.100
This is the way.

04:19.110 --> 04:22.100
I am the light.

04:30.230 --> 04:33.250
[snarling]

04:42.149 --> 04:50.090
[feeding]

04:50.100 --> 04:52.259
[snarling]

04:52.269 --> 04:58.069
[feeding continues]

05:50.240 --> 05:52.170
Hello?

06:04.160 --> 06:07.180
[thunder rolls]

06:19.250 --> 06:21.230
Who are you?

06:24.250 --> 06:27.259
[thunder rolls]

06:40.220 --> 06:43.019
[thunder rolls]

07:12.230 --> 07:16.120
Hey, can you hear me?

07:12.230 --> 07:16.120
Wake up!

07:16.129 --> 07:18.050
Hey, wake up!

07:24.220 --> 07:26.220
Woah, woah, woah,

07:24.220 --> 07:26.220
woah, woah!

07:26.230 --> 07:28.259
You saved us.

07:28.269 --> 07:32.120
I don't know how, but you

07:28.269 --> 07:32.120
freed us from that nightmare.

07:32.129 --> 07:34.220
We can't thank you enough.

07:34.230 --> 07:36.189
You're a saviour.

07:36.199 --> 07:37.209
Thank you.

07:37.220 --> 07:38.230
You're welcome.

07:38.240 --> 07:40.009
You're welcome.

07:45.019 --> 07:46.220
Woah, what're you doing?

07:46.230 --> 07:49.129
Coming with you.

07:50.159 --> 07:53.000
Uh, ok.

07:53.009 --> 07:56.250
Um... you're now immune

07:53.009 --> 07:56.250
to vampirism.

07:56.259 --> 07:57.240
Your blood is actually repulsive

07:56.259 --> 07:57.240
to them

07:57.250 --> 07:59.279
so they won't even want

07:57.250 --> 07:59.279
to drink it.

07:59.290 --> 08:02.009
But that doesn't mean

07:59.290 --> 08:02.009
you can't die.

08:03.139 --> 08:05.170
Got it?

08:05.180 --> 08:08.189
Look, there are others out there

08:05.180 --> 08:08.189
who could really use the help

08:08.199 --> 08:14.120
from people like you

08:08.199 --> 08:14.120
so go find them.

08:14.129 --> 08:16.019
We will.

08:17.040 --> 08:18.209
Ok.

08:19.279 --> 08:21.170
Alright, ok.

08:21.180 --> 08:22.199
Get up.

08:22.209 --> 08:25.129
Up, up, up.

08:25.139 --> 08:26.230
Go.

08:36.000 --> 08:39.049
[fighting grunts]

08:42.149 --> 08:44.039
[groans]

08:46.250 --> 08:48.200
[fighting grunts]

08:48.210 --> 08:49.250
[groans]

08:52.039 --> 08:55.240
I'm getting so much faster.

08:55.250 --> 08:57.149
Don't get cocky.

08:57.159 --> 09:02.049
Speed doesn't mean squat

08:57.159 --> 09:02.049
if you get killed.

09:02.059 --> 09:03.139
Am I tiring you out?

09:03.149 --> 09:04.139
