09:04.149 --> 09:07.039
keep messing up my sleep.

09:07.049 --> 09:08.110
Where'd you score those?

09:08.120 --> 09:11.190
Let's just say your old man

09:08.120 --> 09:11.190
doesn't pay his guys too well.

09:11.200 --> 09:14.039
I got these off the guard

09:11.200 --> 09:14.039
at my door.

09:14.049 --> 09:16.009
For a tube of toothpaste.

09:16.019 --> 09:17.240
I think you need

09:16.019 --> 09:17.240
the toothpaste more.

09:17.250 --> 09:19.049
Ha, ha.

09:19.059 --> 09:20.049
Ready?

09:20.059 --> 09:21.190
For what?

09:21.200 --> 09:23.210
Woah! What're you doing?

09:23.220 --> 09:24.240
I can't see.

09:24.250 --> 09:26.139
That's the point.

09:26.149 --> 09:28.190
Just playing out a hunch.

09:30.169 --> 09:32.250
Where are you, Julius?

09:32.259 --> 09:34.049
This is a little bit

09:32.259 --> 09:34.049
