09:38.190 --> 09:40.090
[cries out]

09:42.159 --> 09:45.149
This is bullshit!

09:45.159 --> 09:47.230
Concentrate.

09:47.240 --> 09:50.159
You don't even know

09:47.240 --> 09:50.159
what you're capable of.

09:51.259 --> 09:53.059
Where are you, Julius?

09:53.070 --> 09:55.059
Focus.

09:55.070 --> 09:57.250
See through the dark.

09:57.259 --> 09:59.159
Yeah right.

09:59.279 --> 10:01.159
[cries out]

10:03.289 --> 10:05.200
[yelps in pain]

10:06.250 --> 10:08.039
[yelps]

10:08.049 --> 10:10.080
I told you I can't      see!

10:11.279 --> 10:13.250
But there's so much

10:11.279 --> 10:13.250
you can do.

10:13.259 --> 10:15.049
[groans]

10:18.240 --> 10:20.230
I can see.

10:20.240 --> 10:22.080
Good.

10:22.090 --> 10:25.220
[fighting grunts]

10:38.110 --> 10:40.250
How did you know I could

10:38.110 --> 10:40.250
do that?

10:40.259 --> 10:43.230
I told you, that bite

10:40.259 --> 10:43.230
had changed you.

10:43.240 --> 10:46.289
I've only ever seen two people

10:43.240 --> 10:46.289
who can do what you do.

10:47.000 --> 10:48.269
Scarlett and Vanessa

10:47.000 --> 10:48.269
Van Helsing.

10:48.279 --> 10:49.269
But I'm not a Van Helsing.

10:49.279 --> 10:52.019
Then why do you heal like one?

10:52.029 --> 10:53.289
Turn vampires human?

10:59.230 --> 11:02.049
Tell me about your mother.

11:02.059 --> 11:04.080
She died.

11:05.080 --> 11:06.259
I'm sorry.

11:14.039 --> 11:16.059
You think my mother was one?

11:16.070 --> 11:19.230
Was she a Van Helsing?

11:19.240 --> 11:23.179
I don't know, but Doc knows

11:19.240 --> 11:23.179
for sure.

11:23.190 --> 11:26.100
Then we go to her.

11:26.110 --> 11:28.110
Believe me, I tried.

11:28.120 --> 11:33.090
Your dad's got her locked up

11:28.120 --> 11:33.090
in here and I can't get to her.

11:33.100 --> 11:35.230
I can.

