12:11.250 --> 12:13.190
[crash]

12:13.200 --> 12:15.149
Son of a bitch.

12:16.029 --> 12:16.289
You spilled my drink.

12:17.000 --> 12:19.200
This pipsqueak is talking

12:17.000 --> 12:19.200
out his ass!

12:19.210 --> 12:22.059
Who gives a shit?

12:22.070 --> 12:26.090
When my wife and kid were

12:22.070 --> 12:26.090
