Now this piece of shit is saying

12:26.100 --> 12:28.289
some woman of the woods

12:29.000 --> 12:31.090
turned him back from being

12:29.000 --> 12:31.090
a vamp.

12:31.100 --> 12:33.190
I ought to kick his ass!

12:35.259 --> 12:38.059
Leave him alone.

12:38.070 --> 12:40.049
Or what?

12:40.059 --> 12:42.009
You really wanna find out?

12:46.230 --> 12:49.039
Shut your mouth!

12:51.039 --> 12:53.220
There ain't no coming back.

12:55.029 --> 12:57.049
I think it's time you take

12:55.029 --> 12:57.049
your shipment and go.

12:57.059 --> 12:58.059
Yeah, yeah.

12:58.070 --> 12:59.269
Thank you.

13:02.230 --> 13:04.289
You're gonna tell me

13:02.230 --> 13:04.289
where she is.

13:20.110 --> 13:21.250
(Sam) Knock, knock.

13:21.259 --> 13:23.210
This is a holy place.

13:23.220 --> 13:26.080
You are not welcome here.

13:28.049 --> 13:29.159
You will die!

13:29.169 --> 13:30.250
[roars]

13:35.039 --> 13:37.210
You.

13:37.220 --> 13:40.080
You're the one that spoke

13:37.220 --> 13:40.080
through me.

13:42.080 --> 13:43.220
We come for her.

13:43.230 --> 13:44.289
What do you want of me?

13:45.000 --> 13:46.019
[laughs]

13:46.029 --> 13:47.179
Not you.

13:47.190 --> 13:48.279
Michaela.

13:48.289 --> 13:50.269
We have sworn to protect

13:48.289 --> 13:50.269
our mother.

13:50.279 --> 13:52.279
We will die first.

13:52.289 --> 13:54.230
Don't tempt me.

13:58.090 --> 14:00.039
Elder.

14:01.289 --> 14:04.100
You have done your job well,

14:01.289 --> 14:04.100
sisters.

14:04.110 --> 14:06.090
The fourth elder

14:04.110 --> 14:06.090
has been anointed

14:06.100 --> 14:09.049
and the time of

14:06.100 --> 14:09.049
the Dark One nears.

14:09.059 --> 14:11.289
We are here to awaken Michaela,

14:12.000 --> 14:15.090
the great mother

14:12.000 --> 14:15.090
of the Sisterhood.

14:15.100 --> 14:17.090
We have been waiting centuries

14:15.100 --> 14:17.090
for this.

14:17.100 --> 14:20.059
Prepare the ritual.

14:26.090 --> 14:29.019
We must be careful.

14:29.029 --> 14:31.230
Michaela is powerful.

14:31.240 --> 14:32.279
Ruthless.

14:32.289 --> 14:34.100
She cannot be trusted.

14:34.110 --> 14:35.259
I like her already.

14:35.269 --> 14:38.210
Do not underestimate her.

14:38.220 --> 14:44.039
Waking her from centuries

14:38.220 --> 14:44.039
in exile will come at a cost.

14:44.049 --> 14:48.000
A cost to us,

14:44.049 --> 14:48.000
or to you?

14:52.259 --> 14:56.289
We are ready

14:52.259 --> 14:56.289
for our mother.

14:57.000 --> 14:59.230
Let us begin.

15:12.110 --> 15:22.250
[Sisters chanting in Latin]

15:34.000 --> 15:43.220
[speaking in Latin]

15:43.230 --> 15:52.259
[speaking in Latin]

15:52.269 --> 16:03.049
