16:03.059 --> 16:14.029
[speaking in Latin intensifies]

16:30.240 --> 16:32.080
[hisses]

16:34.139 --> 16:35.129
Mother.

16:35.139 --> 16:39.070
Rise, Michaela.

16:42.139 --> 16:44.029
Bathory.

16:49.159 --> 16:50.289
[hiss]

16:56.179 --> 16:57.220
Are you sure about this?

16:57.230 --> 16:59.159
Follow my lead.

17:01.029 --> 17:02.169
Sorry, ma'am. No one gets in.

17:02.179 --> 17:03.240
Your father's orders.

17:03.250 --> 17:04.289
We're just here to see a friend.

17:05.000 --> 17:05.289
Not a chance.

17:06.000 --> 17:06.259
Come on, Sid.

17:06.269 --> 17:08.039
A quick in and out,

17:06.269 --> 17:08.039
I promise.

17:08.049 --> 17:09.069
I got orders.

17:09.079 --> 17:11.079
Orders, shmorders.

17:11.089 --> 17:12.220
Is that the 20 pack?

17:12.230 --> 17:14.029
Mmmhmm.

17:15.049 --> 17:16.259
Come on, come on.

17:18.049 --> 17:19.230
And to sweeten.

17:25.059 --> 17:26.180
Five minutes.

17:26.190 --> 17:27.180
Got it?

17:27.190 --> 17:29.000
Thank you.

17:33.009 --> 17:34.230
How is your friend supposed

17:33.009 --> 17:34.230
to help us in here?

17:34.240 --> 17:36.220
I gave her a sample of your

17:34.240 --> 17:36.220
blood before she was locked up.

17:36.230 --> 17:37.230
My blood?

17:37.240 --> 17:38.230
It's ok.

17:38.240 --> 17:40.000
