17:40.009 --> 17:43.180
I got a feeling whatever she

17:40.009 --> 17:43.180
found out is why she's in here.

17:43.190 --> 17:45.200
Oh, look. This is it.

17:45.210 --> 17:47.170
Oh no.

17:49.220 --> 17:50.259
Where is she?

17:50.269 --> 17:53.059
Not your concern.

17:53.069 --> 17:55.039
Take my daughter

17:53.069 --> 17:55.039
to her quarters.

17:55.049 --> 17:56.269
Dad, Julius didn't do

17:55.049 --> 17:56.269
anything wrong.

17:56.279 --> 17:58.279
We'll talk about that later.

18:02.259 --> 18:04.210
Where the hell is Doc?

18:04.220 --> 18:07.009
Where troublemakers go

18:04.220 --> 18:07.009
to learn their place.

18:07.019 --> 18:08.259
I swear to god, if you hurt her

18:07.019 --> 18:08.259
I will rip your-

18:08.269 --> 18:12.259
You'll do nothing.

18:12.269 --> 18:16.000
Violet's taken to you and you

18:12.269 --> 18:16.000
care for her and I see that.

18:16.009 --> 18:18.059
It's what I hoped for.

18:18.069 --> 18:20.019
But I can't have you

18:18.069 --> 18:20.019
filling her head

18:20.029 --> 18:22.099
with mythical stories

18:20.029 --> 18:22.099
and nonsense.

18:22.109 --> 18:25.019
We both know who she really is.

18:27.269 --> 18:29.079
What happened to my daughter?

18:29.089 --> 18:30.170
Ask her.

18:30.180 --> 18:32.039
I'm asking you.

18:32.230 --> 18:33.240
Nothing.

18:33.250 --> 18:35.210
Is that why my men found

18:33.250 --> 18:35.210
the bodies of two vampires

18:35.220 --> 18:37.009
in a dumpster?

18:37.019 --> 18:39.059
What happened?!

18:41.029 --> 18:43.019
They attacked us.

18:43.029 --> 18:44.210
And we handled it.

18:44.220 --> 18:47.180
Isn't that what you wanted?

18:47.190 --> 18:50.250
You said we both knew

18:47.190 --> 18:50.250
who she is.

18:50.259 --> 18:52.190
What'd you mean by that?

18:52.200 --> 18:53.220
[laughs]

18:53.230 --> 18:54.200
Come on.

18:54.210 --> 18:57.000
Now look who's playing dumb.

18:57.279 --> 18:59.089
Hmm.

18:59.099 --> 19:03.109
[choking]

19:23.119 --> 19:25.230
[door closes]

19:33.079 --> 19:34.200
Can I come in, Vi?

19:34.210 --> 19:37.240
It's not like I can stop you,

19:34.210 --> 19:37.240
anyway.

19:37.250 --> 19:39.250
Alright, then I'll cut

19:37.250 --> 19:39.250
right to it.

19:39.259 --> 19:42.069
What were you and Julius doing

19:39.259 --> 19:42.069
in the detention area?

19:42.079 --> 19:43.269
He wanted to see his friend.

19:43.279 --> 19:45.240
And you thought you could

19:43.279 --> 19:45.240
help him with that?

19:45.250 --> 19:47.220
Well, why was she there

19:45.250 --> 19:47.220
in the first place?

19:47.230 --> 19:49.220
You know, this whole Julius

19:47.230 --> 19:49.220
thing was a mistake.

19:49.230 --> 19:51.250
I brought him in because I

19:49.230 --> 19:51.250
thought he'd make you stronger,

19:51.259 --> 19:55.000
but instead I hear about the two

19:51.259 --> 19:55.000
of you sneaking into Low Town,

19:55.009 --> 19:56.269
putting yourselves at risk.

19:56.279 --> 19:58.279
It's not his fault.

20:00.250 --> 20:06.039
Ever since the rising my primary

20:00.250 --> 20:06.039
goal is to protect you.

20:06.049 --> 20:07.079
Keeping me locked

20:06.049 --> 20:07.079
in this compound.

20:07.089 --> 20:08.079
Yes.

20:08.089 --> 20:09.099
That's for my protection?

20:09.109 --> 20:10.150
Yes!

20:10.160 --> 20:12.039
Because I wasn't gonna let

20:10.160 --> 20:12.039
what happened to your sister

20:12.049 --> 20:13.269
happen to you!

20:21.119 --> 20:23.000
You know what?

20:26.069 --> 20:32.000
Yes, I've probably been

20:26.069 --> 20:32.000
a little... overprotective.

20:32.009 --> 20:34.079
That's why I had you train,

20:32.009 --> 20:34.079
so you'd be ready.

20:34.089 --> 20:36.130
Ready for what, exactly?

20:36.140 --> 20:38.059
For anything.

20:38.069 --> 20:41.039
For everything.

20:41.049 --> 20:42.269
Look, I've made some mistakes

20:41.049 --> 20:42.269
and there are things

20:42.279 --> 20:47.210
that I wish had gone differently

20:42.279 --> 20:47.210
but you, Violet,

20:47.220 --> 20:53.059
I wish I could tell you

20:47.220 --> 20:53.059
how important you are to me.

21:23.039 --> 21:25.240
Tell me about my parents.

21:26.289 --> 21:28.079
What's that?

21:28.089 --> 21:31.109
Tell me about my parents.

21:31.119 --> 21:33.150
Oh, come on Violet.

21:33.160 --> 21:38.069
I've told you that

21:33.160 --> 21:38.069
a thousand times.

21:38.079 --> 21:40.289
Make it a thousand and one.

21:43.099 --> 21:45.279
[laughs]

21:47.170 --> 21:49.000
Ok.

21:54.019 --> 21:57.160
They both had brilliant minds

21:57.170 --> 22:02.119
with this desire to make

21:57.170 --> 22:02.119
the world a better place.

22:02.130 --> 22:06.029
We became such close friends.

22:06.039 --> 22:10.170
So much so that they

22:06.039 --> 22:10.170
made me your guardian,

22:10.180 --> 22:17.049
just in case something terrible

22:10.180 --> 22:17.049
happened and it did.

22:17.059 --> 22:20.029
After the accident

22:20.039 --> 22:23.140
the doctors did everything

22:20.039 --> 22:23.140
they could to save them.

22:26.049 --> 22:29.049
I made them a promise.

22:29.059 --> 22:33.250
That I would take care of you.

22:33.259 --> 22:37.140
I failed with your sister.

22:37.150 --> 22:41.029
I am not going to fail with you.

22:55.170 --> 22:58.039
You trust me, right?

22:59.200 --> 23:01.250
Good.

23:01.259 --> 23:04.019
Something you wanna tell me?

23:05.109 --> 23:07.000
No.

23:08.069 --> 23:09.190
Ok.

24:04.089 --> 24:06.190
I know you're there.

24:09.119 --> 24:12.049
It doesn't have to be

24:09.119 --> 24:12.049
this way.

24:13.140 --> 24:18.170
[gun shots]

24:32.180 --> 24:35.150
Ain't no other way it can be.

24:42.240 --> 24:44.200
Go on then.

24:44.210 --> 24:48.230
I told you the next time

24:44.210 --> 24:48.230
I saw you I'd kill you.

24:49.180 --> 24:53.019
Axel, listen.

24:55.150 --> 24:58.069
[groans]

25:11.039 --> 25:12.230
Shit.

25:14.109 --> 25:16.109
